大眼睛做夢，見到的人和物與展現在眼前的完全不同。此刻，他的視線雖然落在隧道的黃色牆壁上，見到的卻是缺乏現代感的「思豪酒店」。站在「思豪酒店」的騎樓上，可以看見雪廠街與木造的渡海小輪碼頭。那木造的渡海小輪碼頭與「思豪酒店」一樣，都不存在了。─《對倒》"},{"pid":"5039606dc974d77bee2da641f59d5231d411b82d","tid":1286003,"uid":72597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:49:52.000Z","msg":"得閒一齊讀下莊梅岩啲劇本，切磋演技又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676e3724d70516b0667120ddddced255c20a9e60","tid":1286003,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cb0f5831348119a3a59b9220f17e274c85f65c5","tid":1286003,"uid":54791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cab9bed87745597534affe576cfa17577e61d472","tid":1286003,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8200737fefef7390e00f7262f7895241d5bf57d3","tid":1286003,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"差啲漏左最緊要嘅，廣東話港產片！<br />\n好多電影好似三五成群、古惑仔、黃秋生啲重口味片(越唔俾越想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) ，呢啲片可以去直播台搵雞寶、thanksyour 台播過嘅嚟介紹俾同學仔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外港產漫畫印象中好似係廣東話口語對白，可以買嚟偷偷地傳閱，只要題材大家鍾意嘅，自然會接受。一兩本書仔唔係貴，既可以推廣本土文化,又可以搞好關係，何樂而不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:42:10.000Z","msg":"成年嘅可以睇叉燒包、貴利王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:47:57.000Z","msg":"屌你叫人地睇叉燒包咁重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇返啲的士判官之類就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:51:52.000Z","msg":"越唔俾睇越想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上面冇得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n伊波拉：恰鳩我？！"},{"pid":"6eec5edf88cae2a477d4b4dea25dbcd97a04d2a0","tid":1286003,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dis